// ColorPicker
// HSV + alpha color picker popover triggered by a color swatch button.
// Provides a 2D saturation/value area, hue slider, alpha slider, and hex
// input. Calls onChange on every interaction and onCommit on close.

FUNCTION rgbToHsv(r, g, b) -> {h, s, v}
  Converts 0-255 RGB to HSV (h: 0-360, s: 0-1, v: 0-1).

---

FUNCTION hsvToRgb(h, s, v) -> {r, g, b}
  Converts HSV back to 0-255 RGB.

---

FUNCTION ColorPicker(color, onChange, onCommit) -> JSX                 EXPORT
  Manages h, s, v, alpha state derived from the color prop on mount.
  Opens/closes a popover anchored to the swatch button.
  Closes on outside click; calls onCommit on close.

---

FUNCTION emitColor() -> void
  Converts current HSV+alpha to RGB Color object and calls onChange.

---

FUNCTION onSvPointerDown(e) -> void
  Captures the pointer for dragging in the SV area.
  Updates s and v from pointer position relative to the SV rectangle.

---

FUNCTION onSvPointerMove(e) -> void
  IF pointer is captured: updates s and v from pointer position.
  Calls emitColor.
